Package cps.mouradalpha.util

Class MyConcurrentHashMap<K,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cps.mouradalpha.util.MyConcurrentHashMap<K,​V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key type
    V - The value type
    public class MyConcurrentHashMap<K,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
    The class MyConcurrentHashMap implements a hash map allowing multiple readers at the same time but only one writer with the help of ReentrantReadWriteLock class. It's used by the Broker in order to manage concurrency between threads who execute read operations and write operations.
    Author:
    Mourad TOUATI / Alpha Issiaga DIALLO
